    "description": "《深渊爬塔》为塔防类 Rogue-lite 游戏，让玩家在科幻的架空世界中，设计属于自己的机械要塞，收集资源、强化改装、不断壮大。<br><br>玩家需要持续为战船升级、加建，在旅程中收集同伴、战斗并掠夺对方的资源，再不断变强。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心玩法１：加建设施</h2><br>要在战船上建立设施，首先要加建底板。当然，底板不能凌空而建。注意，底板不是越多越好，因为建底板会增加战船的面积，令敌人的攻击更易命中，躲避起来更加困难。<br><br>设计好战船后，在底板上建立设施，出发战斗吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/495fd76dd8b1515893ec348fe45a2489.poster.avif?t=1736698203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/495fd76dd8b1515893ec348fe45a2489.webm?t=1736698203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/495fd76dd8b1515893ec348fe45a2489.mp4?t=1736698203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心玩法２：战斗</h2><br>战斗时，玩家需要操控战船移动，以及旋转底板利用战船的自动防卫设施来攻击敌人。击倒敌人会获得资源，让玩家可以进一步加建要塞。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/78476add10393f2c4cd1ca86ff7cd9fc.poster.avif?t=1736698203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/78476add10393f2c4cd1ca86ff7cd9fc.webm?t=1736698203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/78476add10393f2c4cd1ca86ff7cd9fc.mp4?t=1736698203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心玩法３：收集技能</h2><br>每次战斗过后，会随机在遗迹获取电脑图腾 H.O.P.E.，在游戏中帮助玩家。玩家必须善用H.O.P.E.的能力来取得下场胜利。<br><br>本作最有趣的特色，是玩家于每次游戏都会随机得到不同的能力，不能一本通书用到老，要视能力不同而改变玩法，享受每次不同的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/127b5db17b28b5677ac925ec05aa3634.poster.avif?t=1736698203\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/127b5db17b28b5677ac925ec05aa3634.webm?t=1736698203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/127b5db17b28b5677ac925ec05aa3634.mp4?t=1736698203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事简介</h2><br>「生活在沉没深海之下、封闭的超巨形建筑物内部，被称为水下遗迹的地方。女主角亚莉丝是个天才技师。为了解决居住地消失的危机，她独自离乡别井，驾驶自己改造的战船，寻找遗迹的顶部出口，却遭遇迷宫里充满恶意的机械攻击……」<br><br>本作以沉浸在海底的巨大都市、犬懦的居民以及离地的上流阶级，隐喻现代都市的沉沦，带出面对历史的重要。故事中角色的坚持和牺牲，象征微小的无私者企图拯救家园的努力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/50b84586daef2b07245d40af412cb7a7.avif?t=1736698203\" width=600 height=350 /></span><br><br>本作的创作灵感来自《绝对迎击战争》、《沙漠老鼠团改》和《莉迪＆苏瑞的炼金工房》。如果喜欢本作，也请试试这些游戏呢~<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255050/extras/ab02f80cbf212d32dae2f60c045e3402.avif?t=1736698203\" width=600 height=842 /></span>",
